name: Taboo
overview: Adventurer James Keziah Delaney returns to London from Africa in 1814 along with fourteen stolen diamonds to seek vengeance after the death of his father.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: 1814: James Keziah Delaney returns to London from Africa and is encircled by conspiracy, murder and betrayal.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: James Delaney returns to 1814 London after 10 years in Africa to claim a mysterious legacy left to him by his father.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: As James Delaney assembles his league of the damned, an unexpected arrival threatens to disrupt his plans.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: James Delaney decides to take radical action in order to safeguard himself from those intent on his demise.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Blacklisted, James Delaney sets out to protect his business by any means necessary.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: James Delaney is blackmailed into a dangerous mission, whilst animosity between the Crown and Company escalates to a new level.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: The East India Company declares war on James Delaney, whilst a family revelation drives him into dark and haunted places.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: A devastating betrayal puts James Delaneys freedom in jeopardy, handing his enemies the opportunity they've been longing for.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: As James Delaney conspires to escape, an enraged Prince Regent unleashes one final plan to destroy him.
